<h1 class="article-title">
Introduction to open peer review
</h1>
<div class="article-author article-date">
By <a href="http://www.scientificamerican.com/author/hadas-shema">Hadas Shema</a> <span class="metaDataDivider">|</span>
June 28, 2014
</div>
<span class="metaDataDivider">|</span>
<div id="commentsFlairPrint"><a class="tinyCommentCount" data-id="56C4341F-D576-47AE-806A54F66C13C6E4" href="#comments">0</a></div>
